import React from 'react'
import { Box, Button,TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material'

const Contacts = () => {
  
  return (

    <Box style={{textAlign:"center"}}>
<Typography
        variant="h3"
        sx={{ fontSize: "30px", fontWeight: "bold", color: "#000339", my: 2, marginBottom:"40px" }}
      >
        Feel Free To Contact
      </Typography>
  <form 
  action="https://formspree.io/f/xgedgjkr"
  method="POST" style={{ marginLeft:"400px", marginRight:"400px", paddingTop:"20px", paddingBottom:"20px",boxShadow:" 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 6px 20px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19)", marg}} >
<Box style={{justifyContent:"center"}}>
<TextField id="outlined-basic" label="Name" variant='outlined' style={{textAlign:"center", width:"380px"}}/>
</Box>
<Box>
<TextField id="outlined-basic" label="Email" variant='outlined' required style={{textAlign:"center", width:"380px", marginTop:"10px"}}/>
</Box>
<Box>
<TextField id="outlined-multiline-flexible" label="Message" multiline maxRows={4} style={{width:"380px", marginTop:"10px"}} /></Box>
<Box>
<Button variant='contained' style={{marginTop:"10px",width:"380px"}}>SUBMIT</Button>
</Box>
</form>
</Box>
  );
}

export default Contacts
